## Syntax highlighting for emails.

syntax email "\.eml$"

# Quoted lines.
color #AD9 "^>.*"
color #9DD "^> ?>.*"
color #FDA "^> ?> ?>.*"

# Email addresses.
color #CAF "<[^@]+@[^@]+>"

# URLs.
color #8BF "(https?|ftp)://\S+\.\S+[^[:space:].)]"

# Signatures, even quoted ones.
color #FDA start="^>* ?-- $" end="^>* ?$"
